{"tid":660622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角煙廠街女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-05-11T00:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:04:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69cc06a98d4aa4ff0049530393d6510634e1d59c","tid":660622,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:09:51.000Z","msg":"旺角煙廠街一大廈，早上7時，一名40多歲女子從高處墮下，倒臥大廈平台。消防及救護員到場，證實墮樓女人已死亡。警方調查死者身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180511/58177980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58177980&d=E3UvubJckY66CQjiX2yg4IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=203db039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58177980&h=511e13fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180511/58177980</a>"},{"pid":"f4a60fdc607794e999abafdca2e5da5ce2bb62c8","tid":660622,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/photo/bkn-20180511072315153-0511_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180511074500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180511072315153-0511_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180511074500&h=d92943f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子墮樓倒斃平台，遺體由消防移落地面。（葉嘉文攝）<br />\n<br />\n旺角煙廠街一幢大廈，今晨7時許，一名女子被發現由高處墮下，倒斃2樓平台，救護員到場，證實已傷重不治，消防駕起升降台，將遺體運落地面，警員亦用帳蓬遮蓋遺體，正調查其身份及墮樓原因。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n